## Also Create Indexes (for faster Grafana queries)

```sql
CREATE INDEX idx_timestamp ON jmeter_results(timestamp);
CREATE INDEX idx_label     ON jmeter_results(label);
CREATE INDEX idx_created   ON jmeter_results(created_at);
```

